          </a>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="1" height="1" bgcolor="#C2BDB3"></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>&nbsp;</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><table width="90%" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">

      <tr>
        <td colspan="2"><p>Hello <%= @office.user.name %>,</p>
          <p><strong>Thanks for using Intuit Spaces to share your extra office space!
          </strong>We’ll notify you as soon as someone requests your office space.
            In the meantime, sit back, relax and let the renters come to you!</p>
          <p>Here's a convenient link to view your listing: <%= link_to 'View', office_url(@office) %> <br />
            Need to update your listing? Click here <%= link_to "Edit", edit_office_url(@office) %></p>
          <p>Cheers,<br />
            The Intuit Spaces team           </p>
          <p>P.S. If you have any concerns or questions, please email us at <a href="mailto:spaces@intuit.com?subject=Inquiry">spaces@intuit.com</a></p></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
      <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
  </tr>
  </tr>
</table>
